parameters:
...Did you bring that? On the count of three...let's go!
Make sure to synchronize our timing, okay? Alright then, on
the count of three...!!
You're lifting it too much...!! It's tilting, it's tilting!!
Guh...!!! I won't lose to this!!!

Ah, let's stop around here! If we go any further, it might
get in the way.

Hey, is the right side tilting...? Claudia-chan, can you
move it forward just a little bit?
Ah, it feels good...! Just a little more to the right...!!

\SE[15]Wow...!! What a wonderful black shine!! We did it,
didn't we...!! \SE[15]I feel an incredible sense of
accomplishment!!

\SE[24]Haa... haa!! This is absolutely ridiculous...!!
\SE[16]This is something that professionals should be
doing!! It's not something that three children should be
doing with brute force...!!

\SE[16]Oh my... We were able to save some money! But, it's
amazing, you know! Even a strong man couldn't do something
like this!! \SE[10]You can proudly consider it as your
pride!!

\SE[45]Wow, that's amazing. \SE[45]You can have confidence
in your abilities.
\SE[70]A piano in the living room...!? Why!?\. How come!!?

\SE[4]Wow, amazing! \SE[3]Did someone buy this...? \SE[3]But
I wonder if there's anyone who can play it...?

\SE[60]If I thought it was noisy... \!\SE[82]What...
happened,\. with this...?

\SE[46]Did you hear? Vega-chan can play the piano, you know?
\SE[15]That's why I bought it with my big sister money!!

\SE[14]Wow, this is so adult-like...! \SE[13]It's what they
call bulk buying....

\SE[18]... It seems like people have strange expectations of
me. \!\SE[4] I haven't played the piano in years, and I
can't do anything that would impress others. \!\SE[75] I've
forgotten most of the songs too.

\SE[29]Oh no!! I want to hear it!! Please play anything!!
\SE[14]I want to see Vega-chan's wonderful side!!

\SE[14]What...!? Did you just say that Onee-sama is going to
play the piano!? \SE[11]Is such a big event about to
happen...!!?

\SE[52]No, no, at least knock. \SE[53]Even if it's here,
it's rude to just enter someone else's house without
warning...

\SE[4]Wait, you can play the piano!? \!\SE[24]Why didn't you
tell me!? \!\SE[6]Onee-sama, you were keeping a secret from
me!!

\SE[82]No, I just played a little in the past... \SE[83]It's
been years since I had a blank period, so it's not really
worth mentioning...

\SE[4]Wow, what's with this piano? \SE[0]It feels like a
concert is about to start...?

\SE[92]Wow, they're all gathered together... \SE[91]What is
this unprecedented population density...

\SE[16]Isn't it fine?! I worked hard to bring it here, so I
want to hear it!! \!\SE[14]Everyone else wants to hear it
too, right...?!

\SE[0]...Hey. I don't really understand this thing called a
piano.... \!\SE[3]From what I've heard, is it something used
for music?

\SE[20]You don't know about the piano.... \SE[3]...Well,
you're mostly right though.

\SE[59]Well then, I want to see the piano in action. I
carried it here, thinking my arms would be torn off.
\SE[19]...I want to see this child's stage of glory.

\SE[10]Vega, there's no choice but to play in this
situation. With so many people gathered here. \SE[10]To
bring this situation to a close, we have to make a big
impact.

\SE[44]Certainly, there might be no other choice but to do
this...

\SE[60]You can say whatever you want as if it's someone
else's problem...

\SE[22]I get it, I get it!! I just have to play, right? I'll
play!! \SE[20]Even if I'm out of practice, don't you dare
complain!!
\SE[60]Why, how did it come to this...

\SE[15]Ah! I want to listen to the song I heard before!!
\SE[15]I really like that song, you know. It allows me to
reminisce about my youthful days and brings back memories.
\SE[2]Well then, let's change to a different song.
\SE[74]Well... The song I can play now is...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
